dct_description_sm: Shows naval bases, shipping routes, and railways. Uses colors to indicate British, Japanese, USA, French, Netherlands, and other countries' ownership. Insets: 1. Japan -- 2. Nauru -- 3. Ocean Id. -- 4. Hawaiian Islands --5. Midway Id. --6. Phlippine Islands -- 7. Wake -- 8. Canton Id. -- 9. Guam -- 10. Fiji -- 11. Western Samoa -- 12. Eastern Samoa -- 13. Solomon Islands -- 14. Santa Cruz Islands -- 15. New Hebrides British & French Condominium -- 16. New Caledonia Dependencies -- 17. Tahiti -- 18. Lord Howe Id. 19. Norfolk Id. -- 20. Rarotonga -- 21. Yap -- 22. Saipan -- 23. Truk Is. -- 24. Hong Kong -- 25. Singapore -- 26. Malay States. Originally issued folded to 26 x 20 cm.
